Hi I signed up via the Clickbank promo email where it said I'll get a $500 ad credit. I don't see that on my account yet?

Hi Mark, thanks for reaching out! To receive the $500 ad credit from the ClickBank promotion, you need to complete an onboarding call with our Account Managers and go through business verification. You can schedule the onboarding call through this link: [NewsBreak Advertising Consultation](https://calendly.com/d/z4w-3t3-rkw/newsbreak-advertising-consultation). Once these steps are completed, the ad credit should be applied to your account.
